OL,3,CMan murdered partner after drinking 16
OL,4,Cpints of lager and taking cocaine
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurdering his partner after spending
OL,8,Fthe day drinking heavily and taking
OL,9,Fcocaine.
OL,11,FMother-of-two Victoria Thomas, 45, was
OL,12,Ffound dead in a bedroom of a house she
OL,13,Fshared with her partner Alcwyn Thomas
OL,14,Fon August 29, 2024.
OL,16,FThomas, 44, admitted manslaughter but
OL,17,Fmaintained that Victoria's death was a
OL,18,F"sex act gone wrong" and that it was
OL,19,Fduring "erotic asphyxiation" that she
OL,20,Fdied.
