OL,6,FHe denied murder but on Wednesday, 26
OL,7,FMarch, was found guilty of the charge
OL,8,Ffollowing a trial at Cardiff Crown
OL,9,FCourt.
OL,11,FCCTV from the day of Victoria's murder
OL,12,Fshowed that the couple visiting The
OL,13,FNew Inn on Caerphilly Road and then
OL,14,FClub 3000 Bingo in Gabalfa with
OL,15,Fmembers of the defendant's family.
OL,17,FSouth Wales Police said his mood that
OL,18,Fevening was described as argumentative
OL,19,Fand moody, while he had drunk a total
OL,20,Fof 16 pints of lager and had been
OL,21,Fusing cocaine.
