OL,6,FFurther CCTV outside the bingo halls
OL,7,Fcaptured the defendant taking cocaine
OL,8,Fand what appeared to be an argument
OL,9,Fbetween the couple before getting in a
OL,10,Ftaxi.
OL,12,FThe last sighting of Victoria alive
OL,13,Fwas at 9.26pm when the couple returned
OL,14,Fhome.
OL,16,FPolice said that just after 11pm,
OL,17,FThomas sent texts to his sisters,
OL,18,Fsaying "sorry I done something so bad".
