OL,6,FVictoria's body was found during the
OL,7,Fearly hours of August 20 after a
OL,8,Ffamily member, concerned by the texts,
OL,9,Fwent to check on the victim's welfare.
OL,11,FWhen police arrived, Thomas was asleep
OL,12,Fin the couple's bedroom on the middle
OL,13,Ffloor. He replied "no comment" during
OL,14,Fpolice interview but later admitted
OL,15,Fintentionally strangling Victoria.
OL,17,FDetective Chief Inspector Matt Powell,
OL,18,Fsenior investigating officer for South
OL,19,FWales Police, said: "Victoria Thomas
OL,20,Fwas a much-loved daughter, mother,
OL,21,Fsister, aunt, and niece.
