OL,9,Fthoughts are with them today as they
OL,10,Fhave been throughout.
OL,12,F"Having killed Victoria in the spare
OL,13,Fbedroom, Alcwyn Thomas then went to
OL,14,Fsleep in their bedroom.
OL,16,F"At no time, did he make any efforts
OL,17,Fto revive Vicki or seek help for her.
